Class Customer

java.lang.Object
com.plutonian.plutonianProducts.entity.Customer
@Entity
public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
Author:
Steve Bentley Entity class representing the Customer table. Each variable represents a column within the database. Each instance of this class would represent a row. This class is usually used in conjunction with a List to represent many rows.

Please reference Programmers Manual - Detailed requirements for Requirements Tracing - 1.2.4.3, 1.5, 6.1, 6.2, 7.1, 7.2.4, 7.3, 7.4, 8.1.1
